are unique in their crowd control abilities as far as int casters go).  Wis casters job is to buff/heal the melee & int casters (which is why wis casters get gear too, because they need ac and the right-clicky buffs to help them out).  Melee get right clicky buffs to alleviate the begging for buffs from wis casters.  <br><br>I'm tired so this isn't coming out exactly like I'd want it to, but I'm sure you get the point... <p><div align="center"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=56556"><img src="http://superid.homestead.com/files/z-sig.jpg"></a></div></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uzorvad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zorvad</A> at: 3/7/02 6:18:14 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ushadowcross.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shadowcross</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_purplespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/02 6:18:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22661.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/~shadowcross/clip.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Caster robes</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Any casters want to confirm its not just me?</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br><br><br>Well, if you are looking for feedback from other casters, you might be better of asking this question at one of the following caster boards, since we are a rogue board here. There might be some casters around, but you are likely to get more re